162
00:09:54,768 --> 00:09:56,968
Hah? Bagaimana kau tahu?

163
00:09:56,968 --> 00:09:58,368
Seperti yang kuduga.

164
00:09:58,368 --> 00:10:01,668
Pelakunya mungkin orang yang cukup baik.

165
00:10:01,668 --> 00:10:04,768
Apa? Kau tahu siapa pelakunya?

166
00:10:04,768 --> 00:10:06,768
Yah, pelakunya mungkin...

167
00:10:06,768 --> 00:10:08,868
Tunggu, Shinichi!

168
00:10:10,768 --> 00:10:13,668
Aku memiliki deduksiku sendiri.

169
00:10:13,668 --> 00:10:16,868
Jadi, maukah kau mendengarkanku tanpa tertawa?

170
00:10:16,868 --> 00:10:18,468
Silahkan.

171
00:10:18,468 --> 00:10:19,668
Ran.

172
00:10:22,668 --> 00:10:26,568
Biarkan aku mendengarkan deduksimu.

173
00:10:33,031 --> 00:10:35,231
Jadi, itulah deduksiku.

174
